OL,3,CEngland's river health classifications
OL,4,Crelying on old data, campaigners warn
OL,6,FThese species play a vital role in
OL,7,Funderstanding river health because of
OL,8,Ftheir sensitivity to pollution, lower
OL,9,Foxygen levels and habitat degradation.
OL,11,FBut the Environment Agency (EA) has
OL,12,Fbeen relying on samples taken years
OL,13,Fearlier to inform its official river
OL,14,Fhealth classifications, according to
OL,15,Fanalysis of the watchdog's data
OL,16,Fobtained by campaign group WildFish
OL,17,Fthrough freedom of information laws.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
