OL,3,CEngland's river health classifications
OL,4,Crelying on old data, campaigners warn
OL,6,FThe agency carries out invertebrate
OL,7,Fassessments every six years, with
OL,8,Fupdates every three years, under the
OL,9,FWater Framework Directive ` a Europe-
OL,10,Fwide initiative to help water bodies
OL,11,Freach good ecological status and
OL,12,Fprevent deterioration.
OL,14,FThe last major classifications for
OL,15,FEngland's rivers were released in
OL,16,F2019, with the new update for the 2025
OL,17,Fcycle expected soon.
