OL,3,CEngland's river health classifications
OL,4,Crelying on old data, campaigners warn
OL,6,FIn 2019, only 16% of English rivers
OL,7,Fand canals were classed in "good"
OL,8,Fecological health, and none were found
OL,9,Fto be in good chemical health.
OL,11,FHowever, WildFish's analysis found
OL,12,Fthat the EA heavily relied on older
OL,13,Fdata then and may have to again for
OL,14,F2025.
OL,16,FIt argued that the upcoming
OL,17,Fclassifications could therefore
OL,18,Fmislead the public, who may assume the
OL,19,Fmonitoring is based on up-to-date
OL,20,Finformation.
