OL,3,CEngland's river health classifications
OL,4,Crelying on old data, campaigners warn
OL,6,FSam Green, a senior freshwater
OL,7,Fecologist at the environmental group,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We can only take action to save
OL,9,FBritain's rivers when we know what's
OL,10,Fgoing on under the surface, and so a
OL,11,Flack of up-to-date science and a
OL,12,Freliance on rollover data from
OL,13,Fprevious years is deeply concerning."
OL,15,FOf the 3,645 water bodies assessed in
OL,16,F2019, WildFish found that only 1,781
OL,17,Fhad new monitoring for invertebrates `
OL,18,For 52%.
OL,20,FThe rest then used "rolled over" data
OL,21,Ffrom the previous update in 2016.
