OL,3,CEngland's river health classifications
OL,4,Crelying on old data, campaigners warn
OL,6,FAreas with the highest percentage of
OL,7,Fdata rollover were the South West at
OL,8,F63.1%, the South East at 62.6%, and
OL,9,Fthe Humber at 54.0%, while Anglian had
OL,10,Fthe lowest percentage at 39.9%.
OL,12,FAhead of the 2025 update this year,
OL,13,FWildFish said the EA may have to roll
OL,14,Fover some of the same monitoring data
OL,15,Ffrom 2019 again because new samples
OL,16,Fhave still not been taken in the
OL,17,Fintervening years.
