OL,3,CEngland's river health classifications
OL,4,Crelying on old data, campaigners warn
OL,6,FThe researchers used the EA's tool for
OL,7,Fthe latest ecology data to see whether
OL,8,Fnew data had been collected between
OL,9,F2022 and 2024, looking at the upper
OL,10,Fand middle catchment area for the
OL,11,FRiver Test in Hampshire as a case
OL,12,Fstudy.
OL,14,FThey found that only five of the 11
OL,15,Fassessed water bodies in the area have
OL,16,Frecent data.
OL,18,FThe remaining six have data from the
OL,19,F2019 cycle, with five of these dating
OL,20,Fback to 2016.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
