OL,4,Crelying on old data, campaigners warn
OL,6,FFor the River Test's lower and
OL,7,FSouthampton streams operational
OL,8,Fcatchment, WildFish also found that
OL,9,Feight waterbodies will likely be
OL,10,Fassessed using rolled over data, which
OL,11,Famounts to 67% of the operational
OL,12,Fcatchment.
OL,14,FThe data for all eight of these
OL,15,Fwaterbodies was also rolled over in
OL,16,F2019 from the previous cycle in 2016.
