OL,3,CEngland's river health classifications
OL,4,Crelying on old data, campaigners warn
OL,6,FMore widely, this could mean many
OL,7,Friver health assessments across
OL,8,FEngland for the 2025 cycle will be
OL,9,Fbased on old figures, with some dating
OL,10,Fback nearly a decade, WildFish said.
OL,12,FWhile the EA needs more funding and
OL,13,Fresources to carry out robust river
OL,14,Fmonitoring, the group argued that it
OL,15,Fcan reduce its reliance on rollover
OL,16,Fdata with the help of citizen
OL,17,Fscientists through the WildFish
OL,18,FSmartRivers programme, which has seen
OL,19,Fvolunteers collect industry-standard
OL,20,Fdata on rivers across the country
OL,21,Fbiannually for years.
