OL,6,FAn EA spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fworking with many partners including
OL,8,Fcitizen scientists to understand more
OL,9,Fabout our water bodies to help protect
OL,10,Fthe ecosystems and wildlife they
OL,11,Fsupport.
OL,13,F"We are expanding where we monitor and
OL,14,Fthe diversity of data we collect and
OL,15,Four 2025 invertebrate classifications
OL,16,Fwill use new information from over
OL,17,F1,300 monitoring sites across the
OL,18,Fcountry."
