OL,8,FDirective monitoring each year and
OL,9,Fmakes use of suitable data from a host
OL,10,Fof other environment monitoring
OL,11,Fprogrammes it delivers, the
OL,12,Fspokesperson added.
OL,14,F"Where new monitoring data is not
OL,15,Favailable, using the most recent valid
OL,16,Fclassification ensures continuity and
OL,17,Favoids gaps in our understanding of
OL,18,Friver health," they said.
